page.title: 01NORTH WEST OF ST.IVES
page.content: This block of land is northwest of St.Ives.It includes parts of the parishes of Bluntisham and Needingworth.The area contains several farms which are mainly arable. Hensby's Composts is situated in this area.This company specialises in making compost for mushrooms.Anglia Alpines(a wholesale Alpine seller)is also in this area.The B1050,A1123 and B1040 run through this area.Rock meadow kennels(a cat and dog Kennels)is in this area as well.Near Wood Farm is the Bluntisham tip(Cambridgeshire County Council). The routes of several disused railways pass through this region.
